Package jadacz.lib

All classes that work for server and client.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Sendable Interface of classes which can be serialized to packet.
 

Class Summary
Connection Connection is a class used to handle two way comunication and data exchange.
Contact Contact is a class for holding a Contact Object.
FileData Class which allows sending file data.
FileInfo Class represents information about file to send.
LoginRequest Object of this type allows us to log in onto server.
Message Holds all information about message.
Packet Packet is a class used to transfer any data between clients and server.
Status Class which represents user activity status.
UserInfo Class which holds user information.
 

Package jadacz.lib Description

All classes that work for server and client. Jadacz library.
